Requirements:
=============

The documentation is written in DocBook XML V4.2.

Validation and processing the PDF is done with OpenJade using DSSSL
Stylesheets. Used wrappers around OpenJade and JadeTeX are from
docbook-toys.

Processing of man-pages and HTML is done with xsltproc (from libxslt)
using the XSL Stylesheets.

The following versions were tested:

openjade 1.3.1
docbook-dsssl-stylesheets 1.77
docbook-toys 0.61.0
libxslt 1.0.22
docbook-xsl-stylesheets 1.56.1

Remark:
=======

These version are mostly *not* included in SuSE 8.0.
Most of the packets where taken from
ftp://ftp.suse.com:/pub/people/ke/8.0-i386/

The docbook-xsl-stylesheets package may be found at

http://www.theorie.physik.uni-wuppertal.de/~eicker/docbook-xsl-stylesheets-1.56.1-1.noarch.rpm 

Note:
=====

The environment variable SGML_CATALOG_FILES has to be set to:

/var/lib/sgml/CATALOG.docbk42:/var/lib/sgml/CATALOG.db42xml:/var/lib/sgml/CATALOG.jade_dsl:/var/lib/sgml/CATALOG.docbkdsl

